name: UnofficialFliteTest
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Flash Briefing skill that reads off details from the FliteTest website. Currently limited to new products, it may be expanded to new articles very soon! I have to get in touch with FliteTest to see if they have an RSS feed for their articles, look out for that in the future! This is simple, and useful if you don't keep up with the channel!

Disclaimer: This is NOT a FliteTest product and they do not endorse it in any way.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
